==== Ø1" cylindrical lens into indexed rotating mount ====

===== Objects needed =====

*1x ThorLabs part #: ACY254-50-A Ø1" <i>f</i> = 50 mm achromatic cylindrical lens doublet<br />
*1x ThorLabs part #: RSP1X15/M Ø1" indexed rotating mount

